  <li><a href="https://www.cnbcindonesia.com/market/20191107153907-19-113506/saham-perbankan-berguguran">Saham Perbankan berguguran</a> atau</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.cnbcindonesia.com/news/20191107140745-4-113470/pak-jokowi-besok-data-cad-diumumkan-jeblok-lagi-gak-ya">Pak Jokowi, Besok Data CAD Diumumkan! Jeblok Lagi Gak Ya?</a> atau</li>
